SignShop allows you to set up physical shops by punching a chest with your items you want to sell, then punching a sign (while holding redstone dust). It's easy to set up, and even easier to customize!

Want to get involved with the SignShop plugin?  Devinish and Wargamer have been pretty busy as of late, and want your help to continue development.  Send us a message to be part of a plugin consistently used by over 10,000 users.
